decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color:=
 #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> rally in Ga=
meStop Corp.</a>, I =E2=80=A6=C2=A0am not sure I believe that anymore? I am=
 not sure what I do believe. But I am open to the possibility that, like, a=
 major=C2=A0driver of stock-market moves is retail YOLOing of weekly-expiry=
