out that possibility. It makes me want to go back to bed. =E2=80=9CStock pr=
ices discount the expected future cash flows of operating businesses,=E2=80=
=9D naive beginners think, but those who are enlightened=C2=A0know that sto=
ck prices are actually just a side effect of weekly call options, an entert=
aining online gambling product. Why.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway=
 here=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24=
658730.251860/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9yb2Jpbmhvb2Qtc3RvY2stc=
