erday</a>? I guess? Ugh, I don=E2=80=99t know:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;">Investors piled into Robinhood options on their first day o=
f trading Wednesday, helping send the stock up sharply. Robinhood, which ma=
de its debut on Nasdaq last week at $38 a share, closed Wednesday at $70.39=
, an 85% jump from its initial-public-offering price. ...</p><p style=3D"ma=
rgin: 16px 0;">The sharp moves in Robinhood=E2=80=99s share price Wednesday=
