lly damaged" by company executives withholding information and allegations =
that have recently come to light through a California Department of Fair Em=
ployment and Housing (DFEH) discrimination and harassment lawsuit against t=
he company. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To support that claim=
