expect them to have a material adverse effect on our business, financial co=
ndition, results of operations, or liquidity," the suit says.</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That line and similar ones in the filings hide the fac=
t that Activision Blizzard had fielded "numerous complaints about unlawful =
