lt in serious impairments to Activision Blizzard's operations." =E2=80=A6</=
p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[Tuesday]=C2=A0morning, Activision Blizzard =
announced that Blizzard President J. Allen Brack is stepping down after nea=
rly 16 years with the company. That move comes after thousands of Activisio=
n Blizzard employees signed a petition decrying the company's initial respo=
nse to the California lawsuit and hundreds took part in a one-day "Walkout =
for Equality" last week while demanding action on numerous fronts.</p></blo=
ckquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I should say that the Ars Technica art=
